lettering is in fact indented.

151
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:17,100
And of course, the crater
illusion disappears.

152
00:06:17,100 --> 00:06:19,410
Where there are other
depth clues available

153
00:06:19,410 --> 00:06:22,830
like no one would see this face as concave

154
00:06:22,830 --> 00:06:25,590
even though it's lit from
below, because our experience

155
00:06:25,590 --> 00:06:29,790
of faces gives us overriding
information about depth.

